column5: Nope, Couple of good crack of lightning and thunder, looks like a dump of rain coming too.

Nope, Couple of good crack of lightning and thunder, looks like a dump of rain coming too.  Guess my dreams of a Christmas river fish day have been washed away. i,ll still make a nice walk though with the camera in hand.  Will you have a cup of hot joy ,if I stop by?
More like peeling potatoes, sweet potatoes and ramming sumptin into the turkey.. .  You can stop by, only takes a couple minutes to make a java with something special.
A hot cup of java it is.
A hot cup of java it is. See ya when ya get here.
